    <lb n="1"/>Πτολεμαίωι ἰσοτίμωι τοῖς πρώτοις

    <lb n="2"/>φ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ί</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear>οις καὶ στρατηγῶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>

